{"tid":1813413,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「好清息」聰嫂全線停業！","createTime":"2020-01-06T09:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T10:18:44.000Z","uid":69016,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e8ca09be4648fa5a86f9ca85ccc3632320ece3b3","tid":1813413,"uid":69016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T09:07:05.000Z","msg":"早一個禮拜同我老母食飯<br />\n佢對我講 佢有朋友做聰嫂<br />\n佢朋友話 有個股富立咗一大舊錢走咗佬<br />\n無錢到連入貨都成問題<br />\n我嗰陣仲諗啲師奶嘢點會真<br />\n所以就無理到佢<br />\n<br />\n點知啱啱見到蘋果話聰嫂全嫂停線停業<br />\n先發覺 原來成件事有啲料到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200106&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60456245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200106%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60456245&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=7e859dc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200106%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60456245&h=ebbf8738\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200106&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60456245</a><br />\n<br />\n各位手足 唔好畀佢停！<br />\n黃色經濟圈慢慢地見效啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 決一不可<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0b72dc2c1c24c8c42759c20f7142909ab21c85","tid":1813413,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T09:08:13.000Z","msg":"仲有燉炳強、友口腹同泰星真味"},{"pid":"29ea57394b44a7ca578785e1f52fc05e8e5f9d34","tid":1813413,"uid":131122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T09:08:53.000Z","msg":"入邊管理層全部大陸人黎<img src=\"/asse